column16: Eric Hosmer grounds out, second baseman Kelly Johnson to first baseman Adam Lind.
Yuniesky Betancourt singles on a line drive to left fielder Rajai Davis.    Alcides Escobar scores.
Alcides Escobar doubles (3) on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Mitch Maier pops out to third baseman Brett Lawrie.
Chris Gimenez grounds into double play, third baseman Brett Lawrie to second baseman Kelly Johnson to first baseman Adam Lind.    Jeff Keppinger out at 2nd.
Jeff Keppinger singles on a line drive to third baseman Brett Lawrie, deflected by pitcher Sergio Santos.
David Ortiz grounds out, shortstop Yunel Escobar to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Ryan Sweeney singles on a ground ball to right fielder Jose Bautista.    Darnell McDonald scores.    Cody Ross to 3rd.    Ryan Sweeney to 2nd on the throw.
Cody Ross walks.    David Ortiz to 2nd.
Adrian Gonzalez out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Eric Thames.    Dustin Pedroia scores.
Dustin Pedroia doubles (2) on a line drive to left fielder Eric Thames.
Carlos Santana grounds out, second baseman Kelly Johnson to first baseman Adam Lind.
Shin-Soo Choo flies out to left fielder Rajai Davis in foul territory.
Asdrubal Cabrera homers (1) on a fly ball to right field.
Michael Brantley grounds out, pitcher Sergio Santos to first baseman Adam Lind.
Jason Kipnis grounds out, second baseman Kelly Johnson to first baseman Omar Vizquel.
Casey Kotchman grounds out softly, pitcher Sergio Santos to first baseman Omar Vizquel.    Aaron Cunningham to 2nd.
